<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>URGENTE: Multiple Segnalazioni - TableTalk</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #dc3545;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #dc3545;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .urgent-alert {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border: 2px solid #f5c6cb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #721c24;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .urgent-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .urgent-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .urgent-message {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .user-profile {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
        }
        .user-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .user-avatar {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: #dc3545;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }
        .user-info h3 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #dc3545;
        }
        .user-stats {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .reports-list {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .report-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .report-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .report-info {
            flex: 1;
        }
        .report-reporter {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .report-reason {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }
        .report-time {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
            text-align: right;
        }
        .action-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #dc3545;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .warning-box {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #856404;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">üö® TableTalk</div>
            <div class="subtitle">NOTIFICA URGENTE - Richiede Attenzione Immediata</div>
        </div>

        <div class="urgent-alert">
            <div class="urgent-icon">‚ö†Ô∏è</div>
            <div class="urgent-title">ATTENZIONE AMMINISTRATORI!</div>
            <div class="urgent-message">
                L'utente <strong>{{reportedUserNickname}}</strong> ha ricevuto <strong>{{reportCount}} segnalazioni</strong> 
                che richiedono la vostra revisione immediata. Questo pattern potrebbe indicare un comportamento problematico 
                che necessita di intervento tempestivo.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="user-profile">
            <div class="user-header">
                <div class="user-avatar">
                    {{substring reportedUserNickname 0 1}}
                </div>
                <div class="user-info">
                    <h3>{{reportedUserNickname}}</h3>
                    <div class="user-stats">
                        ID: {{reportedUserId}} | {{reportCount}} segnalazioni attive
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="warning-box">
            <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Raccomandazioni:</strong><br>
            ‚Ä¢ Verificare immediatamente il profilo dell'utente<br>
            ‚Ä¢ Controllare la cronologia delle segnalazioni<br>
            ‚Ä¢ Valutare se sono necessarie azioni disciplinari<br>
            ‚Ä¢ Considerare la sospensione temporanea se appropriato
        </div>

        {{#if recentReports.length}}
        <div class="reports-list">
            <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #dc3545;">üìã Ultime Segnalazioni</h3>
            {{#each recentReports}}
            <div class="report-item">
                <div class="report-info">
                    <div class="report-reporter">
                        Segnalato da: <strong>{{this.reporter.nickname}}</strong>
                    </div>
                    <div class="report-reason">
                        Motivo: {{this.reason}}
                        {{#if this.details}}
                        <br>Dettagli: {{this.details}}
                        {{/if}}
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="report-time">
                    {{#if this.createdAt}}
                        {{formatTime this.createdAt}}
                    {{else}}
                        Oggi
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
            </div>
            {{/each}}
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{adminDashboardUrl}}" class="action-button">
                üîç Rivedi Immediatamente nella Dashboard
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>TableTalk - Team di Moderazione</strong></p>
            <p>Questa notifica √® stata inviata automaticamente per segnalazioni multiple.</p>
            <p>Per assistenza immediata, contatta il team tecnico.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
